# Go conventions

- Module: `github.com/alecsavvy/mojave`
- Go 1.25+
- CLI: cobra (`commands/` package)
- Config: `config/` package, loaded from path
- App wiring: `app/` package holds ABCI app with store + content store deps
- State store: `store/` — will be PebbleDB via CometBFT ABCI
- Content store: `content/` — will use gocloud.dev blob.Bucket
- Server: `server/` — will expose ConnectRPC + GraphQL (gqlgen)
- Proto: `proto/` — protobuf definitions, generate with `protoc`
- DDEX types imported from external `ddex-proto` module
- All on-chain state protobuf-encoded
- Errors should wrap with context, not swallow
